<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>True Tap - Advanced Tap-to-Pay for Solana</title>
    <meta name="description" content="True Tap transforms the Solana Seeker into the world's most advanced payment device. Two phones tap together, and money moves instantly.">
    <link rel="icon" href="/logo.png" type="image/png">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8B3D 0%, #FF6B29 50%, #FF4D14 100%);
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .main-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 140px;
            height: 140px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 0 0 2rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin: 0 0 3rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 550px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0 4rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }
        
        .feature {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .feature::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.8) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 100%);
        }
        
        .feature h3 {
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .feature p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            padding-top: 2.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .features {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-container {
                padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            }
            
            .hero-section {
                margin-bottom: 3rem;
            }
            
            .logo {
                width: 120px;
                height: 120px;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }
            
            .features {
                margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
            }
            
            .feature {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .main-container {
                padding: 1rem 0.75rem;
            }
            
            .feature {
                padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-section">
                <img src="/logo.png" alt="True Tap Logo" class="logo">
                <h1>True Tap</h1>
                <p class="tagline">The world's most advanced tap-to-pay experience</p>
                <p class="description">
                    Transform your Solana Seeker into the ultimate payment device. 
                    Two phones tap together, and money moves instantly on the Solana blockchain.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>üöÄ Instant Payments</h3>
                    <p>Tap two phones together for lightning-fast SOL, USDC, and BONK transfers with sub-second confirmation times</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>üîí Secure & Private</h3>
                    <p>Built on Solana with Genesis Token verification for authentic Seeker devices and end-to-end encryption</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>üì± NFC + Bluetooth</h3>
                    <p>Advanced hardware integration combining NFC proximity and Bluetooth LE for seamless peer-to-peer transactions</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <div class="status-badge">
                    üèóÔ∏è In Development for Solana Mobile Hackathon
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>Built for the Solana Mobile Hackathon ‚Ä¢ Optimized for Solana Seeker</p>
                <p>&copy; 2025 True Tap. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>